data.description: Step into this fabulous home that seamlessly blends timeless charm with contemporary comforts in this well maintained  3 bedroom, 2 full baths Cape Cod. The entrance welcomes you with abundant natural light streaming through floor-to-ceiling arched windows, highlighting the tiled fireplace, and pristine hardwood floors t/o the entire first floor. A formal dining room adorned with decorative leaded glass windows leads to an updated kitchen boasting a ceramic tile floor, premium stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, cherry wood cabinets, and a subway tile backsplash.  The first floor hosts a full bath and a versatile bedroom, which can also be utilized as a family room. On the upper level, you'll find a spacious master bedroom featuring a walk-in closet, a modern hall bath, and an additional bedroom with a bonus sitting area, reading nook, or office space. The lower level has a full unfinished basement with a dedicated laundry area.  Step outside from the kitchen to a decent-sized yard with stone paver patio, perfect for outdoor gatherings. Completing the property is a detached one-car garage along with driveway parking. This home is ideally situated within walking distance to the Fox Chase Train Station, schools, shops, and restaurants nearby.  Bonus features include central air, recently replaced roof, recessed lighting and a lovely covered front porch.  This home boasts a ton of character and charm with many of its original features. Come take a look at this beauty and make this home yours first to enjoy just in time for the Holidays!
